He tried his best to hide under the pile of lettuce but it was no use.
What kind of salad has one tomato.
I would almost prefer no tomatoes by that point.
You couldn't throw in some carrot sticks.
I don't even need whole carrots, just some shavings would have been fine.
At least I got a good laugh for my meal at Wendy's.

