Service:  Great.
The servers at the drive thru were nice, and our food was ready for us when we got to the window.
Price:  $10 for two burgers is pretty expensive.. not including drinks or a combo.
Food:  We got two of the new ciabatta bacon cheeseburgers, and I thought they were really good.
I probably won\t buy it again though, just because of the price.

